---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Authority Roadmap" description="Dunstan Research Group credibility roadmap and milestones.">
  <div class="container" style="padding-top:4rem;padding-bottom:4rem;max-width:800px;">
    <h1>Authority Roadmap</h1>
    <p class="page-intro">Our plan for building and maintaining research credibility over time.</p>

    <div style="margin-top:2.5rem;display:grid;gap:1.5rem;">
      <div style="background:var(--color-surface);border:1px solid var(--color-border);border-radius:var(--radius);padding:1.75rem;">
        <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;">
          <h2 style="font-size:1.2rem;">Phase 1 — Foundation</h2>
          <span style="background:var(--color-primary);color:#fff;font-size:0.7rem;padding:0.25rem 0.6rem;border-radius:999px;">Done</span>
        </div>
        <ul style="margin-top:1rem;padding-left:1.5rem;line-height:1.8;color:var(--color-muted);">
          <li>Published methodology and evidence framework</li>
          <li>Named independent reviewer program</li>
          <li>First benchmark and market reports live</li>
          <li>Disclosure, editorial, and correction policies published</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div style="background:var(--color-surface);border:1px solid var(--color-border);border-radius:var(--radius);padding:1.75rem;">
        <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;">
          <h2 style="font-size:1.2rem;">Phase 2 — Depth</h2>
          <span style="background:var(--color-accent);color:#fff;font-size:0.7rem;padding:0.25rem 0.6rem;border-radius:999px;">In Progress</span>
        </div>
        <ul style="margin-top:1rem;padding-left:1.5rem;line-height:1.8;color:var(--color-muted);">
          <li>All reports reviewed by at least one independent PhD-level reviewer</li>
          <li>Annual review cycle for active benchmarks</li>
          <li>Expanded source documentation and archived evidence</li>
          <li>Quarterly transparency reports on corrections and updates</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div style="background:var(--color-surface);border:1px solid var(--color-border);border-radius:var(--radius);padding:1.75rem;">
        <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;">
          <h2 style="font-size:1.2rem;">Phase 3 — Scale</h2>
          <span style="background:#6B7280;color:#fff;font-size:0.7rem;padding:0.25rem 0.6rem;border-radius:999px;">Future</span>
        </div>
        <ul style="margin-top:1rem;padding-left:1.5rem;line-height:1.8;color:var(--color-muted);">
          <li>Additional active categories</li>
          <li>Archived report versioning</li>
          <li>API access to published datasets</li>
          <li>External advisory board</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 style="margin-top:3rem;">Quarterly Targets</h2>
    <ul style="margin-top:1rem;padding-left:1.5rem;line-height:1.9;">
      <li>Publish at least one category benchmark or market report per quarter.</li>
      <li>Maintain zero pay-to-rank or pay-to-validate arrangements.</li>
      <li>Respond to all correction submissions within five business days.</li>
      <li>Update all featured benchmarks at least annually.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
